QP_Pmf                  Computes the probability mass function of the
                        scores.
QP_Probability          Computes the probability of a score.
QP_Pvalue               Computes the p-value of a score.
QP_SigPvalue            Computes the p-value for a statistically
                        significant score.
QP_Support              Computes the support for the scores.
QuaternaryProd-package
                        Computes the Quaternary Dot Product Scoring
                        Statistic for Signed and Unsigned Causal Graphs
RunCRE_HSAStringDB      This function runs a causal relation engine by
                        computing the Quaternary Dot Product Scoring
                        Statistic, Ternary Dot Product Scoring
                        Statistic or the Enrichment test over the Homo
                        Sapien STRINGdb causal network (version 10
                        provided under the Creative Commons license:
                        https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/).
                        Note that the user has the option of specifying
                        other causal networks with this function.
